details.name: Street Race - Up Your Alley
details.creator: RSGIND_CastroA
details.desc: Careering down the alleyways of Mission Row, you'll always find one of three things. 1) A mugging. 2) A handjob. 3) A street race shortcut. Fingers crossed for number three and/or number two. Lap race for Los Santos Tuners.
